Contribution Sovereignty Economy (CSE) v0.2

Compression

“Compensation follows contribution.”

“Infrastructure earns continuously.”

“Trust is measurable.”

“Extraction without value trends toward zero.”

⸻

Core Observation

Current economies mix multiple things into “money”:

Money acts simultaneously as:

1. Exchange medium
2. Value storage
3. Reputation proxy
4. Trust proxy
5. Scarcity allocation
6. Coordination mechanism
7. Power accumulation mechanism

Problem:

When these collapse together:

Capital → Capital → More Capital

can begin to outgrow:

Contribution → Reward

Not always. But enough to create frustration.

